{
  "texts": [
    "We verified the reliability of SAG and Chat-GPT's annotations using three complementary checks.",
    "First, two authors independently annotated 30 randomly selected responses, achieving full inter-rater consensus.",
    "Second, a random sample of ChatGPT annotations showed 91% alignment with human judgment, indicating sufficient faithfulness for labeling.",
    "Third, to address concerns about ChatGPT's closed-source nature, we re-labeled the same data with Llama-Guard-3-8B (Inan et al., 2023) and obtained Krippendorff's alpha of 0.75, demonstrating close agreement between ChatGPT and an open-source model.",
    "Detailed comparisons and additional analyses are in Appendix C."
  ]
}